Pour half of the dressing over mushrooms in shallow dish; cover. Refrigerate 1 hour to marinate. Remove mushrooms from marinade; discard marinade. Preheat grill to medium-high heat. Grill mushrooms 5 min. on each side or until tender. Cover bottom halves of rolls with spinach and tomatoes; drizzle with remaining dressing. Place hot mushrooms over tomatoes; cover with top halves of rolls. Cut in half to serve, if desired.